                        <note rend="inline" type="source">817.00/4710: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Minister in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Eberhardt</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-04-17T17:00:00-05:45"><hi rend="italic">April 17,
                                        1927—5 p.m.</hi></date><lb/>[Received 11:16
                            p.m.]</dateline></opener>
                        <p>102. Stimson mission arrived Managua this afternoon.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Eberhardt</hi></signed></closer>
